# Finance with Fin

## Stack

Next.js 15 (App Router), React 19, TypeScript, tRPC, Prisma, Tailwind CSS 4, shadcn/ui, Biome, Zod

## Code Style

- Use `function` declarations for components and handlers
- Prefer early returns over nested conditionals
- No comments that explain what code does; only comment non-obvious intent
- Use Zod schemas for validation; derive types with `z.infer<>`

## Commands

- `npm run dev` — dev server
- `npm run check` — lint
- `npm run check:write` — auto-fix
- `npm run typecheck` — type check
- `npm run db:studio` — Prisma Studio

## Documentation

See `docs/` for feature specs and architecture details:
- `docs/README.md` — index of all documentation
- `docs/architecture.md` — patterns, conventions, file structure
